data.description: Beautifully home features new roof in 2020, bamboo floors, mosaic tile bathroom, 4 bedrooms plus a bonus room. The open kitchen boasts a large island and high quality appliances, seamlessly connecting to the inviting living room with a cozy fireplace. The spacious master bedroom offers a custom-built walk in closet. The garage has been transformed into a finished bonus room with abundant storage and its own entrance, complete with a television, built in surround sound and a convenient kitchenette. Enjoy the covered sunroom, expansive fenced yard with a campfire pit, deck with a gazebo and convenient RV parking!  Ample parking space and lush trees provide shade. Appliances are included  Close to JBLM. Buyer's financing fell through.
